headline: Fed Rate Move, Apple Earnings, Trump-Xi Meeting: What to Watch Next Week
summary: Investors next week will tune into big-tech earnings and the first Federal Reserve meeting since the U.S. government shutdown began. Later in the week, President Trump is due to meet with Chinese leader Xi Jinping as trade tensions between the two economic giants simmer.
